l, since many host cities build new venues for the Games.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many host cities\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"new venues\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cast your mind back toLondon 2012, for example, and the opening of theQueen Elizabeth Olympic Park, which haslived on post-Olympicsas a green space and multi-purpose sports facility, as well as being the home ofWest Ham Unitedand the hugely popular ABBA Voyage.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"theQueen Elizabeth Olympic Park\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicsas\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"a green space\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"multi-purpose sports facility\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"the home\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"Ham Unitedand\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the hugely popular ABBA Voyage\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But not every purpose-built Olympic venue has such impressive afterlife, with some abandoned altogether once the last medal had been won\\u2026 The 1936 Olympics in Berlin were notorious, taking place in the shadow of Adolf Hitler's Nazi regime and its horrific ideals of racial supremacy and antisemitism.\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"score\": 0.999999974943876, \"rank\": 2.50559249775842e-08, \"text\": \"Berlin\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin\"}, {\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 906, \"title\